  "session": "2026RS",
  "identifier": "HB 213",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to reemployment of retired police officers.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 70.292, 70.293, and 95.022, regarding city and county programs to reemploy retired police officers without incurring employer retirement contributions, to reduce the required service of the officer or sheriff before retirement from 20 years to 15 years and to allow retired officers to take health insurance coverage through the employing city or county; amend KRS 61.702 and 78.5536 to conform.",
